rts.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2F2011-world-cup-winning-team-was-united-not-sure-about-this-one-harbhajan-singh-4458707%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2F2011-world-cup-winning-team-was-united-not-sure-about-this-one-harbhajan-singh-4458707%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Hamas%20Outfoxed%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%2C%20A%20Nearly%20Impenetrable%20Air%20Defence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20at%20war%20following%20an%20unprecedented%20attack%20by%20the%20Hamas%20group.%20Over%205%2C000%20rockets%20were%20fired%20towards%20Israel%20from%20the%20Hamas-controlled%20Gaza%20Strip%20in%20just%2020%20minutes%20after%20it%20declared%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisraels-forces-say-ready-for-war-after-rocket-attacks-by-gaza-4458496%5C%22%3EOperation%20Al-Aqsa%20Flood%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAir%20raid%20sirens%20across%20Israel%20shattered%20the%20morning%20silence%20and%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20system%2C%20one%20of%20the%20best%20air%20defence%20systems%20in%20the%20world%2C%20was%20again%20in%20action.%20In%20dramatic%20visuals%2C%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20destroyed%20rockets%20mid-air%20and%20the%20sky%20was%20illuminated%20with%20bursts%20of%20flares.%20This%20time%2C%20however%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20attack%20was%20unprecedented.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20system%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Iron%20Dome%20system%20is%20a%20ground-to-air%20short-range%20air%20defence%20system%20deployed%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20to%20counter%20rocket%20attacks%2C%20mortars%2C%20artillery%20shells%2C%20and%20Unmanned%20Aerial%20Vehicles%20(UAVs)%20at%20short%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20defence%20system%20has%20a%20range%20of%20approximately%2070%20km%20and%20has%20three%20central%20components%20that%20form%20a%20unit%2C%20namely%3B%20Detection%20and%20Tracking%20radar%2C%20Battle%20Management%20and%20Weapons%20Control%20and%20the%20Missile%20Launcher%20armed%20with%2020%20Tamir%20Missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20has%20guarded%20Israel%20since%202011.%20During%20the%202006%20Lebanon%20conflict%2C%20thousands%20of%20rockets%20were%20fired%20by%20Hezbollah%20and%20several%20northern%20areas%20including%20Haifa%20were%20attacked%2C%20killing%20many.%20The%202006%20attacks%20prompted%20Israel%20to%20develop%20its%20own%20air%20defence%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Iron%20Dome%20Works%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20rocket%20is%20fired%20toward%20Israel%2C%20the%20Detection%20and%20Tracking%20radar%20detects%20the%20incoming%20trajectory%20and%20relays%20the%20information%20to%20the%20weapons%20control%20system%2C%20which%20performs%20fast%2C%20complex%20calculations%20to%20detect%20the%20trajectory%2C%20speed%20and%20expected%20target%20of%20the%20rocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20incoming%20rocket%20is%20directed%20towards%20a%20populated%20area%20or%20a%20strategic%20establishment%2C%20the%20launcher%20automatically%20fires%20the%20Tamir%20Missile%20and%20the%20rocket%20is%20destroyed%20mid-air%20to%20neutralize%20the%20threat.%20A%20single%20battery%20consists%20of%20three-four%20launchers%20and%20Israel%20has%20at%20least%2010.%20The%20manufacturer%20of%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20system%20-%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rafael.co.il%2Fworlds%2Fair-missile-defense%2Fshort-range-air-missile-defense%2F%5C%22%3E%20Rafael%20Advanced%20Defence%20System%3C%2Fa%3E%20claims%20it%20has%20a%20success%20rate%20of%2090%20per%20cent%20and%20has%20over%202%2C000%20interceptions%20till%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Happened%20This%20Time%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20near-perfect%20air%20defence%20system%20found%20itself%20overpowered%20after%20a%20barrage%20of%20rockets%20from%20Hamas.%20For%20several%20years%2C%20the%20terrorist%20group%2C%20Hamas%2C%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20weakness%20in%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20system.%20They%20have%20been%20largely%20successful%20in%20doing%20so%20by%20overwhelming%20the%20system%20with%20a%20Salvo%20rocket%20attack%20(multiple%20rockets%20launched%20in%20a%20short%20span%20of%20time)%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20control%20system%20to%20intercept%20all%20targets.%20This%20time%2C%20over%205%2C000%20rockets%20were%20launched%20in%20just%2020%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20is%20continuously%20developing%20its%20crude%20rocket%20technology%20and%20over%20the%20years%20it%20has%20increased%20its%20range%20to%20cover%20major%20cities%20of%20Israel%20including%20Tel%20Aviv%20and%20even%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20rocket%20launched%20by%20Hamas%20is%20much%20cheaper%20than%20the%20Tamir%20missile%20fired%20to%20intercept%20it.%20For%20Israel%2C%20the%20Iron%20Dome's%20worth%20extends%20its%20cost%20analysis.%20It%20has%20proven%20itself%20in%20the%20past%20that%20it%20can%20neutralise%20targets%20and%20save%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmissilethreat.csis.org%2Fdefsys%2Firon-dome%2F%23easy-footnote-bottom-12-89%5C%22%3EDuring%20a%20conflict%20with%20Hamas%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202012%2C%20Israel%20claimed%20that%2085%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20400%20rockets%20fired%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20toward%20civilian%20and%20strategic%20areas%2C%20were%20countered.%20During%20the%202006%20Lebanon%20conflict%20over%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202014%20conflict%2C%20over%204%2C500%20rockets%20were%20fired%20by%20Hamas%20over%20several%20days.%20Over%20800%20were%20intercepted%20and%20around%20735%20were%20shot%20down%2C%20a%20success%20rate%20of%2090%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpgrade%20and%202021%20Attacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Israel%20said%20it%20had%20upgraded%20the%20system%20to%20cope%20with%20additional%20aerial%20threats%20including%20successful%20interceptions%20of%20rocket%20and%20