nced%20something%20of%20a%20miracle%20as%20her%20cancer%20vanished%20after%20doctors%20prescribed%20a%20new%20wonder%20drug.%20Carrie%20Downey's%20stage%20three%20bowel%20cancer%20disappeared%20within%20six%20months%20of%20taking%20the%20drug%2C%20dostarlimab%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-wales-67028925%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2042-year-old%20civil%20servant%20was%20diagnosed%20a%20year%20ago%20and%20given%20dostarlimab%20infusions%20for%20six%20months.%20Tests%20have%20shown%20there%20is%20no%20longer%20any%20evidence%20of%20the%20disease%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsbuhb.nhs.wales%2Fnews%2Fswansea-bay-health-news%2Ffirst-person-in-wales-to-get-cancer-wonder-drug-is-given-the-all-clear%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESwansea%20Bay%20University%20Health%20Board%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20news%20release.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDostarlimab%20targets%20a%20specific%20variant%20of%20colorectal%20cancer.%20While%20it%20is%20still%20being%20clinically%20trialled%2C%20it%20is%20already%20showing%20remarkable%20results%20%E2%80%93%20avoiding%20surgery%2C%20radiotherapy%20or%20chemotherapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDostarlimab%20is%20a%20form%20of%20immunotherapy%2C%20a%20targeted%20treatment%20which%20helps%20the%20immune%20system%20destroy%20the%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Downey%20was%20having%20pains%20from%20a%20previous%20hernia%20mesh%20implant.%20While%20investigating%2C%20doctors%20discovered%20her%20cancer.%20She%20was%20diagnosed%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20referred%20to%20Dr%20Craig%20Barrington%2C%20a%20consultant%20oncologist%20at%20Singleton%20Hospital%20in%20Swansea.%20Dr%20Barrington%20prescribed%20dostarlimab.%20She%20was%20put%20on%20dostarlimab%20for%20six%20months%2C%20with%20each%20three-weekly%20IV%20administration%20taking%20around%2030%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20tired%20and%20had%20a%20rash%20here%20and%20there%2C%20but%20nothing%20compared%20to%20chemotherapy%2C%20radiotherapy%20or%20surgery%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20Swansea%20Bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPartway%20through%20her%20treatment%2C%20scans%20showed%20the%20tumour%20had%20shrunk%20significantly.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20course%2C%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20of%20the%20disease.%20Two%20subsequent%20scans%20have%20confirmed%20this%2C%20the%20release%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20single%20mother%20with%20a%2017-year-old%20son%20is%20preparing%20to%20return%20to%20work%20after%20her%20successful%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20so%20thankful%20to%20Dr%20Barrington%20and%20his%20team%20that%20I%20got%20the%20chance%20and%20that%20he%20had%20looked%20into%20the%20mutation%20and%20looking%20at%20these%20new%20therapies%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20given%20me%20my%20life%20back.%20I%20will%20be%20forever%20grateful%20to%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%2018%20rectal%20cancer%20patients%20were%20given%20the%20same%20drug%20for%20six%20months%20and%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20treatment%2C%20cancer%20was%20completely%20obliterated%20in%20every%20patient.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696732680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F0j2gpd6o_carrie-downey-_625x300_08_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-declared-all-clear-from-cancer-thanks-to-miracle-drug-4460688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2042-year-old%20civil%20servant%20was%20diagnosed%20a%20year%20ago%20and%20given%20dostarlimab%20infusions%20for%20six%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-declared-all-clear-from-cancer-thanks-to-miracle-drug-4460688%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-declared-all-clea