irst%20two%20hours%20of%20%E2%80%9COppenheimer%E2%80%9D%20were%20electrifying.%20I%20felt%20the%20kind%20of%20full-scale%20mind%2Fsoul%20immersion%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fcolumns%2Fthe-secret-weapon-of-oppenheimer-christopher-nolan-cillian-murphy-1235747908%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fcolumns%2Fthe-secret-weapon-of-oppenheimer-christopher-nolan-cillian-murphy-1235747908%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fcolumns%2Fthe-secret-weapon-of-oppenheimer-christopher-nolan-cillian-murphy-1235747908%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Vehicles%2C%20Boats%2C%20Paragliders%3A%20How%20Hamas%20Breached%20Gaza%20Security%20Barrier%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHamas%20terrorists%20--%20travelling%20in%20vehicles%2C%20boats%20and%20motorised%20paragliders%20--%20breached%20Gaza's%20security%20barrier%20and%20attacked%20nearby%20Israeli%20towns%20and%20military%20posts%2C%20opening%20fire%20on%20residents%20and%20passersby.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGun%20battles%20raged%20into%20the%20night%20as%20at%20least%2070%20people%20were%20reported%20killed%20in%20Israel%2C%20while%20Gaza%20authorities%20released%20a%20death%20count%20of%20232%20in%20the%20conflict's%20bloodiest%20escalation%20in%20years%20which%20also%20left%20many%20hundreds%20wounded%20on%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20said%20in%20the%20evening%20its%20forces%20were%20still%20engaged%20in%20live%20gun%20battles%20in%2022%20locations%2C%20in%20an%20ongoing%20operation%20labelled%20%26quot%3BSwords%20of%20Iron%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20reservists%20were%20being%20called%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20still%2022%20locations%20where%20we%20are%20engaging%20with%20terrorists%20that%20came%20into%20Israel%2C%20from%20the%20sea%2C%20from%20the%20land%20and%20from%20the%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20army%20spokesman%20Richard%20Hecht%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20included%20a%20%26quot%3Brobust%20ground%20invasion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20earlier%20released%20images%20of%20several%20Israelis%20taken%20captive%2C%20and%20another%20Israeli%20army%20spokesman%2C%20Daniel%20Hagari%2C%20confirmed%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20kidnapped%20soldiers%20and%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20give%20figures%20about%20them%20at%20the%20moment.%20It's%20a%20war%20crime%20committed%20by%20Hamas%20and%20they%20will%20pay%20the%20price.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20at%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20told%20the%20stunned%20nation%20as%20the%20airforce%20pounded%20targets%20in%20the%20blockaded%20coastal%20enclave%2C%20including%20several%20residential%20tower%20blocks%20that%20were%20completely%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20enemy%20will%20pay%20an%20unprecedented%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20veteran%20premier%20vowed%20after%20Hamas%20had%20launched%20its%20first%20such%20combined%20ground%2C%20air%20and%20sea%20offensive%2C%20half%20a%20century%20after%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%201973%20Arab-Israeli%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Islamist%20group%20started%20the%20multi-pronged%20attack%20around%206%3A30%20am%20(0330%20GMT)%20with%20thousands%20of%20rockets%20aimed%20as%20far%20as%20Tel%20Aviv%20and%20Jerusalem%2C%20some%20bypassing%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20defence%20system%20and%20hitting%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSend%20help%2C%20please!%26quot%3B%20one%20Israeli%20woman%20sheltering%20with%20her%20two-year-old%20child%20pleaded%20as%20terrorists%20outside%20opened%20fire%20and%20tried%20to%20break%20into%20their%20safe%20room%2C%20Israeli%20media%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBodies%20were%20seen%20lying%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Sderot%20near%20Gaza%20and%20inside%20cars%2C%20their%20windscreens%20shattered%20by%20bullets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20saw%20many%20bodies%2C%20of%20terrorists%20and%20civilians%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20man%20who%20gave%20his%20name%20as%20Shlomi%20told%20AFP%2C%20standing%20beside%20covered%20corpses%20on%20a%20road%20near%20Gevim%20Kibbutz%20in%20southern%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20many%20bodies%2C%20so%20many%20bodies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Gates%20of%20hell'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20army%20Major%20General%20Ghasan%20Alyan%20warned%20that%20Hamas%20had%20%26quot%3Bopened%20the%20gates%20of%20hell%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20AFP%20journalist%20in%20Gaza%20saw%20smoke%20billowing%20from%20the%20remains%20of%20a%20residential%20tower%20which%20Gaza's%20interior%20ministry%20said%20contained%20100%20apartments%20and%20was%20completely%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20it%20had%20warned%20residents%20to%20evacuate%20before%20targeting%20the%20multi-storey%20buildings%20used%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20aid%20group%20Doctors%20without%20Borders%20said%20one%20strike%20had%20hit%20the%20enclave's%20Indonesian%20hospital%20and%20an%20ambulance%20outside%20Nasser%20Hospital%20in%20southern%20Gaza%2C%20causing%20multiple%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20night%20fell%2C%20Israel's%20state-run%20electricity%20company%20cut%20the%20power%20supply%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20escalation%20follows%20months%20of%20rising%20violence%2C%20mostly%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20tensions%20around%20Gaza's%20border%20and%20at%20contested%20holy%20sites%20in%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20labelled%20its%20attack%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Al-Aqsa%20Flood%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20on%20%26quot%3Bresistance%20fighters%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20in%20%26quot%3BArab%20and%20Islamic%20nations%26quot%3B%20to%20join%20the%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20decided%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20all%20the%20crimes%20of%20the%20occupation%20(Israel)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20its%20armed%20wing%2C%20the%20Ezzedine%20al-Qassam%20Brigades%2C%20claiming%20to%20have%20fired%20more%20than%205%2C000%20rockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHecht%20said%20Israel%20had%20counted%20more%20than%203%2C000%20incoming%20rockets%20though%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20chief%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20claimed%20the%20group%20was%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bverge%20of%20a%20great%20victory%20and%20a%20clear%20conquest%20on%20the%20Gaza%20front%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEnough%20is%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20televised%20address.%20%26quot%3BThe%20cycle%20of%20intifadas%20(uprisings)%20and%20revolutions%20in%20the%20battle%20to%20liberate%20our%20land%20and%20our%20prisoners%20languishing%20in%20occupation%20prisons%20must%20be%20completed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Dangerous%20precipice'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAir%20raid%20sirens%20wailed%20across%20southern%20and%20central%20Israel%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20where%20multiple%20incoming%20rockets%20were%20intercepted%20by%20air%20defence%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20a%20gaping%20hole%20was%20ripped%20into%20a%20building%2C%20with%20residents%20boarding%20a%20bus%20to%20seek%20safety%20in%20a%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERocket%20impacts%20left%20cars%20burning%20beneath%20residential%20buildings%20in%20the%20Israeli%20city%20of%20Ashkelon%2C%20north%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20dead%20was%20the%20president%20of%20a%20regional%20council%20for%20Israeli%20communities%20northeast%20of%20Gaza%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20gun%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESchools%20will%20remain%20closed%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20start%20of%20the%20week%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20sparked%20major%20disruption%20at%20Tel%20Aviv%20airport%2C%20with%20American%20Airlines%2C%20Emirates%20and%20Ryanair%20am