ood%20that%20was%20hit%20by%20rockets%20Saturday%20(left).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65217f169f7ca8b2bbdcd96e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221039%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETour%20guide%20Ziv%20Cohen%20stands%20guard%20in%20his%20town%2C%20Mazkeret%20Batya%2C%20where%20some%20homes%20were%20hit%20by%20rockets.%3Cp%3EZiv%20Cohen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EIsraeli%20officials%20called%20on%20armed%20civilians%20to%20guard%20their%20towns%20following%20attacks%20by%20Hamas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHamas%20launched%20an%20attack%20from%20Gaza%20on%20Saturday.%20Israel%20has%20since%20declared%20a%20%26quot%3Bstate%20of%20war.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EZiv%20Cohen%2C%20a%20tour%20guide%20from%20Mazkeret%20Batya%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20civilians%20who%20volunteered%20to%20stand%20guard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EZiv%20Cohen%20woke%20up%20at%20about%206%3A30%20a.m.%20on%20Saturday%20to%20the%20rumble%20of%20someone%20moving%20furniture%20in%20the%20apartment%20above%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%2C%20suddenly%2C%20after%20it%20continued%20again%20and%20again%2C%20it%20came%20to%20my%20head%20that%20I'm%20on%20the%20top%20floor%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20one%20above%20me%20to%20move%20a%20chair.%20It%20was%20an%20attack.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%2C%2054%2C%20was%20actually%20hearing%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idf.il%2Fen%2Farticles%2Fhafatzot%2Freal-time-updates-07-10%2F%5C%22%3Ebarrages%20of%20rockets%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20launched%20early%20Saturday%20by%20Hamas%2C%20the%20political%20and%20military%20organization%20governing%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20that%20the%20United%20States%20designates%20a%20terrorist%20organization.%20The%20attack%20has%20so%20far%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-declares-state-of-war-hamas-launches-massive-surprise-attac