%20that%20their%20young%20sons%20were%20among%20three%20people%20killed%20in%20a%20plane%20crash%20in%20Canada%20a%20day%20earlier.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-trainee-pilots-from-mumbai-among-3-killed-in-canada-plane-crash-4460201%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-trainee-pilots-from-mumbai-among-3-killed-in-canada-plane-crash-4460201%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-trainee-pilots-from-mumbai-among-3-killed-in-canada-plane-crash-4460201%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gunmen%20At%20Door%2C%20Bodies%20On%20Road%3A%20Hamas'%20Sabbath%20Attack%20Shocks%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBloodied%20bodies%20in%20the%20streets%2C%20gunmen%20raiding%20door-to-door%2C%20and%20news%20of%20captives%20taken%20to%20Gaza%20left%20Israelis%20terrified%20and%20in%20shock%2C%20after%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20surprise%20attack%20that%20was%20unprecedented%20in%20audacity%20and%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20resident%20reported%20seeing%20multiple%20bodies%20and%20bullet-scarred%20vehicles%20in%20the%20southern%20Israeli%20town%20of%20Sderot%20where%20groups%20of%20Hamas%20gunmen%20were%20still%20fighting%20Israeli%20troops%2012%20hours%20after%20the%20attack%20was%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20out%2C%20I%20saw%20loads%20of%20bodies%20of%20terrorists%2C%20civilians%2C%20cars%20shot%20up.%20A%20sea%20of%20bodies%2C%20inside%20Sderot%20along%20the%20road%2C%20other%20places%2C%20loads%20of%20bodies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shlomi%20from%20Sderot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20night%20fell%2C%20at%20least%20100%20were%20reported%20dead%20and%20more%20than%201%2C000%20wounded%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20media%2C%20with%20fighting%20still%20raging%20in%20more%20than%2020%20locations%20around%20the%20Gaza%20St