nt%20group%20has%20ruled%20the%20tiny%20Gaza%20Strip%20since%20winning%20local%20elections%20in%202006.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20designated%20Hamas%20a%20foreign%20terrorist%20organization%20in%201997.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20political%20and%20military%20organization%20that%20governs%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-declares-state-of-war-hamas-launches-massive-surprise-attack-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaunched%20a%20wave%20of%20unprecedented%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Israel%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2070%20people%20in%20Israel%20have%20so%20far%20been%20killed%20and%20more%20than%20900%20injured%20since%20the%20attacks%20began%2C%20the%20Israeli%20authorities%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20Saturday%20that%20Israel%20was%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bstate%20of%20war%26quot%3B%20and%20promised%20an%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%26quot%3B%20retaliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20retaliation%20has%20already%20begun.%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%20on%20the%20densely%20populated%20Gaza%20Strip%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Flive%2F2023%2F10%2F07%2Fworld%2Fisrael-gaza-attack%2F05a259c8-5b44-5a9d-a4dc-aad8caee8f8f%3Fsmid%3Durl-share%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleveled%20a%20high-rise%20apartment%20building%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday.%20And%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAP%2Fstatus%2F1710651831104180251%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Palestinian%20Health%20Ministry%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%20200%20Palestinians%20have%20so%20far%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20is%20Hamas%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%20is%20designated%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20due%20to%20repeated%20armed%20attacks%20inside%20Israel%20by%20means%20of%20suicide%20bombings%20and%20rocket%20attacks%2C%20among%20other%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%26quot%3B%20is%20an%20acronym%20for%20Harakat%20al-Muqawama%20al-Islamiya.%20It%20was%20founded%20by%20Sheikh%20Ahmed%20Yassin%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20religious%20leader%20who%20became%20an%20activist%20in%20the%20Muslim%20Brotherhood.%20Yassin%20created%20Hamas%20as%20the%20Muslim%20Brotherhood's%20political%20arm%20in%20Gaza%20in%201987%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfr.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Fwhat-hamas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECouncil%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Washington-based%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Favalon.law.yale.edu%2F20th_century%2Fhamas.asp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20a%20charter%20in%201988%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20included%20a%20call%20to%20%26quot%3Bobliterate%26quot%3B%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20and%20to%20install%20a%20new%20Islamic%20society.%20The%20charter%20was%20amended%20in%202017%2C%20although%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpalwatch.org%2Fstorage%2Fdocuments%2Fhamas%2520new%2520policy%2520document%2520010517.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20still%20does%20not%20recognize%20Israel%20as%20a%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20first%20designated%20Hamas%20a%20foreign%20terrorist%20organization%20in%201997%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20State%20Department.%20The%20organization%20has%20ruled%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20since%202006%20after%20beating%20its%20rival%20political%20party%2C%20Fatah%2C%20in%20local%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Hamas%20takeover%20of%20Gaza%2C%20Israel%20instituted%20a%20blockade%20of%20the%20small%20sliver%20of%20land%20that%20has%20now%20lasted%20for%2016%20years.%20The%20blockade%20restricts%20the%20flow%20of%20goods%20into%20the%20Palestinian%20territory%20and%20has%20caused%20shortages%20of%20everything%20from%20food%20to%20medicine.%20It%20also%20largely%20restricts%20Palestinians%20from%20leaving%20Gaza.%20The%20blockade%20has%20devastated%20the%20local%20economy.%20Half%20the%20population%20of%20Gaza%20is%20unemployed%2C%20presenting%20fertile%20recruitment%20for%20Hamas%20military%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surprise%20attack%20on%20Saturday%20was%20the%20deadliest%20since%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E2014%2C%20when%20the%20murder%20of%20three%20Israeli%20teenagers%20by%20Hamas%20sparked%20a%20seven-week%20retaliation%20from%20Israel.%20The%20violence%20caused%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Fworld-report%2F2015%2Fcountry-chapters%2Fisrael%2Fpalestine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20deaths%20of%20about%202%2C100%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDozens%20of%20Israelis%20%E2%80%94%20most%20of%20them%20soldiers%20%E2%80%94%20were%20also%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202021%2C%20tensions%20in%20Jerusalem%20led%20to%20more%20violence%2C%20during%20which%20Hamas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-iron-dome-blocks-90-percent-rockets-hamas-gaza-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaunched%20about%201%2C600%20rockets%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20attack%2C%20Israel's%20%26quot%3BIron%20Dome%26quot%3B%20missile%20defense%20system%20intercepted%20about%2090%25%20of%20the%20projectiles%20fired%20into%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces%20said%20at%20the%20time.%20The%20defense%20system%20uses%20its%20own%20rockets%20to%20destroy%20incoming%20missiles%20before%20they%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20land%2C%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20and%20Egypt%20helped%20to%20negotiate%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-hamas-agree-to-ceasefire-after-bloodiest-fighting-in-years-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecease-fire%20between%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3