gh%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Victorian%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthew%20Goodman%2C%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BEighty%20Days%3A%20Nellie%20Bly%20and%20Elizabeth%20Bisland's%20History-Making%20Race%20Around%20the%20World%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESteamships%20and%20seasickness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20leg%20of%20Bly's%20trip%20was%20aboard%20the%20%26quot%3BAugusta%20Victoria%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20brand-new%20ship%20with%20stained%20glass%2C%20shuffleboard%20games%2C%20and%20starlit%20concerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20she%20was%20crossing%20from%20New%20York%20to%20London%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2F2023-atlantic-hurricane-season-questions-answered-faqs-storm-names-2023-6%5C%22%3EAtlantic%20hurricane%20season%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sea%20travel%20could%20still%20be%20dangerous.%20Everything%20from%20icebergs%20to%20collisions%20with%20other%20vessels%20to%20shipboard%20fires%20presented%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221997%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%2019th%20century%20ocean%20liner%20in%20the%20water%20of%20New%20York%20Harbor%20near%20the%20Statue%20of%20Liberty%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651e296d617692f0d03fa2ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221498%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Augusta%20Victoria%20sails%20past%20the%20Statue%20of%20Liberty%20in%20New%20York%20Harbor.%3Cp%3EHenry%20Guttmann%20Collection%2FHulton%20Archive%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Bly%20and%20Bisland%2C%20seasickness%20proved%20the%20biggest%20hazard.%20The%20ship's%20captain%20recommended%20Bly%20keep%20eating%20until%20the%20nausea%20passed.%20It%20didn't%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20takes%20a%20bite%2C%20and%20she%20runs%20over%20to%20the%20deck%20and%20keeps%20vomiting%2C%26quot%3B%20Behn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%2019th-century%20seasickness%20%26quot%3Bcures%26quot%3B%20included%20%3Ca%20rel%3D