Fryalw5ag6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20Saturday%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20IDF%20has%20been%20warning%20for%20months%20about%20a%20reduction%20in%20readiness%2C%20a%20decrease%20in%20deterrence%20capability%2C%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20multi-front%20flare-up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20responded%20by%20disdainfully%20dismissing%20those%20concerns%20and%20by%20pouring%20gasoline%20on%20the%20fire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetanyahu's%20judicial%20reforms%2C%20which%20were%20proposed%20in%20January%20and%20eventually%20passed%20in%20July%2C%20seek%20to%20limit%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20power%20to%20exercise%20judicial%20review%20and%20declare%20legislation%20unconstitutional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sparked%20significant%20backlash%2C%20with%20opposition%20to%20the%20changes%20cautioning%20that%20Israel%20was%20sleepwalking%20into%20a%20dictatorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20last%20month%20accused%20those%20protesting%20against%20his%20reforms%20of%C2%A0%20%26quot%3Bjoining%20forces%20with%20the%20PLO%20and%20Iran%2C%26quot%3B%20characterizing%20them%20as%20being%20anti-Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20among%20the%20opposition%20was%20a%20vocal%20chorus%20of%20critics%20warning%20that%20the%20civil%20unrest%20stemming%20from%20the%20controversial%20reforms%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20series%20of%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fcabinet-delays-decision-on-palestinian-prisoner-visits-despite-ben-gvirs-insistence%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erogue%20policies%20on%20Palestinian%20prisoners'%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20would%20have%20severe%20security%20repercussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20last%20month%2C%20opposition%20leader%20Yair%20Lapid%20warned%20that%20Israel%20was%20%26quot%3Bapproaching%20a%20violent%2C%20multi-front%20confrontation%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Flapid-netanyahu-has-lost-control-o