t-least-15-dead-and-40-injured-12978962%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Judges%20Have%20to%20Adapt%20to%20Technology%2C%20Says%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F09134529%2Faa-Cover-au7mok02br0m258dgrfuqgmvt0-20200611145151.Medi_.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20that%20judges%20do%20not%20have%20the%20option%20of%20saying%20they%20are%20not%20tech-friendly%2C%20asking%20all%2025%20high%20courts%20in%20the%20country%20to%20have%20video%20conferencing%20(VC)%20facilities%20within%20two%20weeks%20to%20conduct%20hearings%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20person%20personal%20aversion%20of%20judges%20towards%20technology%20cannot%20%E2%80%9Cretrograde%E2%80%9D%20the%20judiciary%E2%80%99s%20digital%20push.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20question%20is%20not%20whether%20a%20particular%20judge%20is%20tech-friendly%20or%20not.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20be%20a%20judge%20in%20this%20country%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20tech-friendly%E2%80%A6%20know%20technology.%20There%20is%20no%20choice.%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20you%20cannot%20say%20as%20a%20judge%20that%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20a%20%3Cem%3Eres%20judicata%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20or%20what%20interpretation%20of%20statutes%20mean%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20bench%2C%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fwant-to-be-a-judge-adapt-to-technology-says-sc-101696619866343.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20courts%20were%20directed%20to%20put%20in%20place%20the%20necessary%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20includes%20Internet%20facilities%20for%20lawyers%20and%20litigants%20who%20appear%20in%20person.%20The%20bench%2C%20also%20consisting%20of%20Justices%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20added%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CTechnology%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20choice%20anymore%20and%20all%20judges%20must%20realise%20it.%20It%20is%20as%20much%20a%20part%20of%20our%20legal%20system%20and%20resources%20as%20the%20law%20books%20are.%20Without%20technology%2C%20how%20do%20you%20function%3F%20Every%20judge%20in%20the%20system%20has%20to%20be%20trained.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdistressed%E2%80%9D%20to%20learn%20that%20many%20high%20courts%20have%20ditched%20the%20VC%20facility%20even%20as%20the%20Union%20government%20sanctioned%20Rs%207%2C210%20crore%20for%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20the%20eCourts%20mission%2C%20under%20which%20digital%20infrastructure%20is%20getting%20a%20boost.%20The%20plan%20is%20to%20set%20up%202%2C500%20new%20modern%2C%20virtual-friendly%20courts%20and%20the%20establishment%20of%201%2C150%20virtual%20courts%20and%204%2C400%20eSewa%20kendras%20in%20all%20court%20complexes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20lapse%20of%20two%20weeks%20of%20this%20order%2C%20no%20high%20court%20shall%20deny%20access%20to%20VC%20facility%20or%20hearing%20through%20the%20hybrid%20mode%20to%20any%20member%20of%20the%20bar%20or%20a%20litigant%20desirous%20of%20availing%20of%20such%20facility.%20All%20state%20governments%20shall%20provide%20necessary%20funds%20to%20the%20high%20courts%20to%20put%20in%20place%20requisite%20facilities%20within%20the%20time%20frame%20as%20indicted%20above.%20The%20high%20courts%20shall%20ensure%20that%20adeaquate%20Internet%20and%20WiFi%20are%20available%20free%20of%20cost%20to%20all%20members%20of%20the%20bar%20and%20litigants%20appearing%20before%20the%20high%20court%20in%20person%2C%E2%80%9D%20recorded%20the%20court%20order%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696675544000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F09134529%2Faa-Cover-au7mok02br0m258dgrfuqgmvt0-20200611145151.Medi_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%