ster.%20If%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20chief%20minister%2C%20MPs%2C%20and%20MLAs%20pledge%20to%20limit%20their%20salaries%20to%20Rs%204%2C000%20per%20month%2C%20we%20will%20conclude%20our%20protest%20and%20ask%20for%20no%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20organised%20by%20the%20All%20India%20Democratic%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Association%20(AIDWA)%20%E2%80%93%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20have%20received%20much%20attention%20from%20the%20mainstream%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFalma%20Chauhan%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEver%20since%202014%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20a%20sharp%20rise%20in%20violence%20against%20women%20in%20this%20%E2%80%98naya%20Bharat%E2%80%99.%20Prices%20are%20sky%20high%2C%20food%20items%20have%20become%20so%20expensive.%20We%20also%20want%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20declare%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20a%20disaster%20zone!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20horrifying%20rape%20of%20women%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20murder%20of%20their%20family%20members%20afterwards%20shows%20us%20the%20hollowness%20of%20his%20%3Cem%3EBeti%20Bachao%2C%20Beti%20Padhao%3C%2Fem%3E%20slogan.%20Our%20women%20wrestlers%20sat%20right%20here%20in%20protest%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20and%20they%20still%20haven%E2%80%99t%20received%20justice.%20Every%20day%20women%20are%20being%20assaulted%2C%20young%20girls%20are%20getting%20raped.%20Kindly%20spare%20us%20your%20hollow%20slogans%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20try%20to%20fool%20us%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKoyal%20Vishvas%20from%20West%20Bengal%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20demands%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20limited%20to%20the%20demands%20of%20women%2C%20they%20are%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20entire%20nation.%20This%20government%20is%20selling%20off%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20institutions%20to%20private%20players.%20The%20rich%20are%20getting%20richer%20and%20the%20poor%20poorer.%20Even%20as%20oil%20prices%20dip%20internationally%2C%20our%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20prices%20continue%20to%20rise.%20What%20is%20this%20government%20up%20to%3F%20Please%20also%20understand%20that%20in%20asking%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%2C%20we%20are%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20asking%20for%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20entire%20nation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FYH1Pm_0fjQg%3Fsi%3DPn9oytaj8_ACmxKp%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Ftax-as-confiscation-modi-governments-k-shaped-policy-proves-keynes-right%5C%22%3EModi%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Development%20Model%3A%20The%20Poor%20Forced%20to%20Eat%20Less%2C%20While%20the%20Rich%20Make%20Merry%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20protest%2C%20many%20women%20sang%20and%20performed%20local%20dances%20from%20their%20home%20states%20in%20small%20groups.%20Some%20of%20them%20were%20carrying%20their%20children%20in%20their%20laps%20as%20they%20danced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20women%20dancing%20at%20the%20protest%2C%20Mariam%20Dhawale%2C%20AIDWA%20general%20secretary%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9COur%20women%20are%20fighters%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explained.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20songs%20they%20are%20singing%20and%20dancing%20to%20are%20the%20songs%20of%20liberation%2C%20justice%2C%20and%20of%20building%20a%20new%20world.%20Dancing%20is%20an%20expression%20of%20the%20joy%20of%20belonging%20to%20the%20world%20and%20winning%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20explained%20how%20AIDWA%20prepared%20for%20months%20for%20this%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20presence%20in%2026%20states.%20For%20the%20last%20many%20months%20we%20have%20conducted%20thousands%20of%20meetings%2C%20scooter%