d%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20Associated%20Press%20news%20agency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20it%20has%20retaliated%20by%20hitting%20targets%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDefence%20minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20has%20approved%20the%20mobilisation%20of%20reservists%2C%20a%20defence%20ministry%20spokeswoman%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%20DPA%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIDF%20troops%20are%20fighting%20the%20enemy%20at%20every%20location.%20I%20call%20on%20all%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20citizens%20to%20follow%20security%20instructions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gallant%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20State%20of%20Israel%20will%20win%20this%20war.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20Israeli%20residents%20who%20have%20completed%20military%20service%20are%20assigned%20to%20the%20reserve%20force%20to%20provide%20reinforcements%20during%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20said%20the%20surprise%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20represents%20a%20massive%20intelligence%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Israeli%20military%20spokesperson%20Lt.%20Col.%20Richard%20Hecht%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Flive%2F2023%2F10%2F07%2Fworld%2Fisrael-gaza-attack%2Fb50c7f24-ae4d-5e2a-a813-34e4216e2129%3Fsmid%3Durl-share%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20security%20forces%20are%20responding%20tactically%20but%20%E2%80%9Cin%20a%20composed%20manner%E2%80%9D%20and%20is%20in%20a%20state%20of%20%E2%80%9Creadiness%20for%20war%E2%80%9D.%20The%20military%20was%20not%20yet%20calling%20the%20events%20on%20Saturday%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwar%2C%E2%80%9D%20despite%20defence%20minister%20Gallant%E2%80%99s%20official%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20we%20know%20about%20the%20attack%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPalestinian%20militants%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20fired%20dozens%20of%20rockets%20at%20I