l-declares-state-of-alert-for-war-as-rockets-from-gaza-hit-country-123100700272_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-declares-state-of-alert-for-war-as-rockets-from-gaza-hit-country-123100700272_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-declares-state-of-alert-for-war-as-rockets-from-gaza-hit-country-123100700272_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Findings%20of%20IIT%20Delhi%20Survey%2C%20a%20Glimpse%20of%20Hostility%20That%20Bahujan%20Students%20Face%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F19152640%2FIIT_-_Delhi_-_Entrance.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20past%20months%2C%20two%20students%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Ftwo-dalit-students-suicides-in-two-months-highlight-institutionalised-discrimination-at-iits%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAnil%20Kumar%20and%20Ayush%20Ashna%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20of%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Delhi%20died%20by%20suicide.%20Both%20students%2C%20barely%2020%20years%20old%2C%20belonged%20to%20the%20Dalit%20community.%20Following%20these%20two%20deaths%20in%20the%20institution%2C%20the%20Board%20for%20Student%20Publications%20(BSP)%2C%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20official%20media%20body%2C%20initiated%20a%20campus-based%20survey%20on%20caste%20discrimination.%20It%20had%20to%20be%20withdrawn%20within%20a%20week%20as%20many%20students%20found%20it%20%E2%80%9Cinsensitive%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cirrelevant%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20more%20than%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20similar%20survey%20was%20conducted%20by%20the%20media%20body%20and%20the%20results%20are%20telling.%20The%20survey%20%E2%80%93%20based%20on%20545%20responses%20from%20undergraduate%20students%20%E2%80%93%20shows%20that%20two%20out%20of%20every%20three%20students%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98general%20category%E2%80%99%20felt%20that%20%E2%80%9Cstudents%20who%20belong%20to%20the%20reserved%20classes%20get%20undue%20advantages%20in%20IITD%E2%80%9D.%20The%20%E2%80%98general%20category%E2%80%99%20consists%20mostly%20of%20students%20from%20savarna%20caste%20groups%20and%20some%20from%20religious%20minorities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStudents%20from%20both%20savarna%20and%20Bahujan%20%E2%80%93%20those%20belonging%20to%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20%E2%80%93%20groups%20were%20surveyed.%20The%20Board%20for%20Student%20Publications%20claims%20that%20permission%20was%20not%20given%20for%20the%20survey%20to%20be%20published%20on%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20website%20and%20hence%20the%20findings%20remained%20under%20wraps%20for%20more%20than%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20disturbing%20findings%20of%20the%20survey%20shows%20that%20one%20in%20two%20%E2%80%9Cgeneral%20category%E2%80%9D%20respondents%20admitted%20to%20making%20casteist%20comments%20intentionally%20or%20unintentionally.%20Of%20them%2C%20nearly%2015%25%20admitted%20to%20having%20intentionally%20passed%20casteist%20comments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20many%20Bahujan%20students%2C%20the%20road%20to%20IITs%20was%20the%20first%20space%20where%20they%20encountered%20casteism.%20Over%2023%25%20of%20students%2C%20the%20survey%20said%2C%20faced%20casteism%20while%20preparing%20for%20JEE%2C%20the%20entrance%20exam%20for%20IITs.%20Over%2014%25%20of%20the%20participants%20shared%20that%20they%20encountered%20casteism%20after%20coming%20to%20IIT.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20several%20cases%20of%20acute%20casteism%20and%20the%20deaths%20of%20students%20from%20the%20Bahujan%20communities%20due%20to%20institutional%20problems%20have%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20at%20different%20IITs.%20While%20the%20institution%20has%20refused%20to%20take%20responsibility%2C%20such%20surveys%20give%20a%20sense%20of%20the%20hostility%20and%20difficult%20environment%20that%20students%20have%20to%20navigate%20through.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Finterview-merit-iit-caste-discrimination-vipin-veetilg%5C%22%3EInterview%20%7C%20%E2%80%98There%20Is%20Nothing%20Meritorious%20about%20IITs%2C%E2%80%99%20Says%20Prof%20Who%20Resigned%20Over%20Casteism%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%2018-year-old%20IIT%20Bombay%20student%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fiit-bombay-darshan-solanki-suicide%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDarshan%20Solanki%20died%20by%20suicide%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20February%20this%20year%2C%20the%20university%20set%20up%20a%2012-member%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20cause%20of%20his%20death.%20The%20committee%20later%20came%20out%20with%20a%20controversial%20report%2C%20individualising%20his%20death%2C%20blaming%20his%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%20scores%E2%80%9D%20and%20completely%20disregarding%20the%20rampant%20casteism%20prevalent%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fiit-bombay-suicide-did-authorities-fail-to-act-even-after-surveys-pointed-to-rampant-casteism%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efirst%20revealed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20different%20IIT%20Bombay%20bodies%3Cspan%3E%2C%20including%20the%20SC-ST%20student%20cell%2C%20had%20conducted%20multiple%20surveys%20towards%20the%20end%20of%202021.%20These%20brought%20out%20the%20insensitive%2C%20hostile%20and%20discriminatory%20atmosphere%20on%20campus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20IIT%20Delhi%20survey%20was%20conducted%20in%20early%202020%2C%20according%20to%20students%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20survey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20campuses%2C%20like%20most%20other%20premier%20institutions%20in%20India%2C%20have%20failed%20to%20take%20corrective%20measures%20to%20change%20the%20environment%20on%20campus.%20Instead%2C%20as%20seen%20recently%2C%20IIT%20Bombay%20and%20IIT%20Hyderabad%20have%20set%20up%20segregated%20%E2%80%9Cvegetarian%20spaces%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20mess.%20A%20student%20who%20protested%20against%20the%20%E2%80%9Cveg-only%20tables%E2%80%9D%20decision%20was%20fined%20Rs%2010%2C000.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F10115234%2FMB-knowledge-tree.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IIT%20Bombay.%20Credit%3A%20University%20website%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F10115234%2FMB-knowledge-tree.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F10115234%2FMB-knowledge-tree-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F10115234%2FMB-knowledge-tree-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-278024%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIIT%20Bombay.%20Photo%3A%20University%20website%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20Board%20for%20Student%20Publications%20shows%20that%2050%25%20of%20students%20from%20SC%2FST%20communities%20felt%20that%20students%20intentionally%20pass%20casteist%20comments.%20In%20the%20survey%2C%20when%20savarna%20students%20were%20asked%20questions%20about%20casteism%2C%20some%20claimed%20they%20faced%20%E2%80%9Ccasteist%20comments%E2%80%9D.%20This%2C%20the%20study%20says%2C%20shows%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdefinition%20mismatch%E2%80%9D%20among%20students%20belonging%20to%20different%20caste%20groups.%20This%20mismatch%2C%20research%20scholars%20who%20were%20a%20part%20of%20the%20survey%2C%20say%20comes%20from%20how%20students%20from%20different%20caste%20locations%20look%20at%20caste%20and%20discrimination.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20savarna%20caste%20student%20will%20happily%20be%20a%20part%20of%20an%20anti-reservation%20WhatsApp%20group.%20He%20won%E2%80%99t%20mind%20making%20casteist%20comments%20on%20the%20group.%20But%20if%20he%20finds%20out%20about%20a%20Bahujan%20student%20becoming%20a%20part%20of%20an%20anti-caste%20social%20media%20group%2C%20he%20will%20cry%20hoarse%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20PhD%20student%20at%20IIT%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20research%20scholar%20pointed%20out%20some%20limitations%20of%20the%20survey.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20survey%20fails%20to%20recognise%20instances%20of%20%E2%80%98positive%20discrimination%E2%80%99.%20It%20groups%20terms%20used%20for%20marginalised%20groups%20and%20privileged%20groups%20as%20%E2%80%98casteism%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20He%20further%20added%20that%20assertions%20by%20those%20from%20marginalised%20identities%20too%20have%20been%20categorised%20as%20casteist%20behavior%20%E2%80%93%20without%20understanding%20the%20context%20in%20which%20those%20statements%20were%20made%20or%20understood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20the%20students%20but%20also%20professors%20and%20administrative%20staff%20who%20indulge%20in%20casteism%2C%20the%20survey%20claims%20%E2%80%93%2011%25%20of%20students%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20survey%20claimed%20to%20know%20of%20%E2%80%9CIITD%20Professors%2Fadministrative%20staff%20who%20have%20made%20casteist%20comments%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20many%20face%20caste-based%20discrimination%2C%20only%20a%20handful%20are%20able%20to%20speak%20up%2C%20the%20survey%20indicates.%20Three%20out%20of%20four%20students%20from%20the%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20categories%20are%20negatively%20affected%20by%20casteist%20comments%2C%20the%20survey%20finds.%20While%2059%25%20of%20the%20savarna%20students%20choose%20to%20remain%20neutral%20to%20the%20casteist%20atmosphere%2C%2041%25%20expressed%20that%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Cnegatively%20impacted%E2%80%9D%20too.%20Of%20the%20students%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20survey%2C%20only%2020%25%20said%20they%20were%20able%20to%20oppose%20casteism%20when%20they%20encountered%20it.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20large%20chunk%20of%20the%20savarna%20students%20expressed%20their%20displeasure%20against%20facilities%20made%20available%20to%20those%20from%20the%20Bahujan%20caste%20categories.%20Over%2060%25%20said%20they%20felt%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20unfair%E2%80%9D%20that%20people%20have%20to%20pay%20different%20fees%20based%20on%20their%20(caste)%20categories.%20Close%20to%2060%25%20found%20facilities%20like%20the%20book%20bank%20made%20available%20to%20students%20belonging%20to%20reserved%20categories%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunfair%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20a%20similar%20questionnaire%20was%20sent%20out%20to%20students%20from%20across%20caste%20groups%2C%20the%20last%20question%20was%20visible%20only%20to%20those%20who%20filled%20OBC%2C%20SC%20or%20ST%20as%20their%20category.%20From%20these%20communities%2C%20215%20students%20responded.%20Of%20them%2C%2052%25%20belonged%20to%20OBC%20communities%20and%2048%25%20belonged%20to%20SC%20and%20ST%20communities%2C%20the%20survey%20notes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20those%20who%20responded%20to%20the%20last%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9C68%25%20of%20the%20reserved%20category%20respondents%20from%20metro%20cities%20felt%20that%20their%20achievements%20were%20undervalued%20as%20compared%20to%2024%25%20from%20a%20small%20village.%E2%80%9D%20A%20similar%20trend%2C%20the%20survey%20points%20out%2C%20can%20be%20observed%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20negatively%20affected%20when%20I%20hear%20a%20casteist%20comment%E2%80%9D%20option%20and%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20hesitant%20in%20disclosing%20my%20rank%2Fcaste%20in%20front%20of%20other%20people%20in%20my%20first%20year%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20survey%20says%2088%25%20of%20the%20SC%20population%20and%2074%25%20of%20the%20ST%20population%20were%20hesitant%20to%20talk%20about%20their%20rank%20or%20caste%2C%20while%20the%20same%20is%20true%20for%2046%25%20of%20the%20OBC%20population.%20From%20the%20results%2C%20it%20can%20be%20inferred%2C%20the%20survey%20report%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20students%20from%20the%20reserved%20categories%20feel%20undervalued%20and%20are%20negatively%20affected%20when%20someone%20makes%20a%20casteist%20comment%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696659946000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F19152640%2FIIT_-_Delhi_-_Entrance.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fiit-delhi-survey-glimpse-hostility-caste-discrimination%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20the%20disturbing%20findings%20of%20the%20survey%20shows%20that%20one%20in%20two%20%E2%80%9Cgeneral%20category%E2%80%9D%20respondents%20admitted%20to%20making%20casteist%20comments%20intentionally%20or%20unintentionally.%20Of%20them%2C%20nearly%2015%25%20admitted%20to%20having%20intentionally%20passed%20casteist%20comments.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fiit-delhi-survey-glimpse-hostility-caste-discrimination%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20militants%20enter%20Israel%20after%20rocket%20barrage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696659338000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F410F%2Fproduction%2F_131355661_7264e491274c19fe9a1d47759ba6acc0a2b946ca464_526_1220_6871220x687.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67036625%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thousands%20of%20rockets%20were%20launched%20towards%20Israel%2C%20Hamas%20says%2C%20with%20one%20person%20reported%20dead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4406%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67036625%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67036625.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67036625.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rockets%20launched%20from%20Gaza%20streak%20across%20sky%20towards%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696657103000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F649B%2Fproduction%2F_131355752_p0gk0y4g.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67037806%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Video%20footage%20shows%20rockets%20fired%20from%20Gaza%2C%20and%20the%20aftermath%20of%20strikes%20on%20Ashkelon%2C%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-middle-east-67037806%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NewsClick%20Case%3A%20%E2%80%98Never%20Received%20Funds%20From%20a%20Foreign%20Govt%E2%80%99%2C%20Says%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%E2%80%99s%20Company%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F07105239%2F5mtb93eo_neville-roy-singham-1200_625x300_07_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Worldwide%20Media%20Holdings%20(WMH)%2C%20the%20US-based%20for-profit%20group%20whose%20investment%20in%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20Delhi%20police%E2%80%99s%20terror%20case%20against%20the%20news%20portal%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Chas%20never%20received%20any%20funding%2C%20nor%20taken%20direction%20from%20any%20foreign%20individual%2C%20organisation%2C%20political%20party%2C%20or%20government%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%2C%20issued%20by%20WMH%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20Jason%20Pfetcher%2C%20seeks%20to%20%E2%80%9Cset%20the%20record%20straight%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20investment.%20The%20Delhi%20police%20arrested%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20editor%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20the%20portal%E2%80%99s%20HR%20head%20Amit%20Chakravarty%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdelhi-police-terror-fir-against-newsclick-names-chinese-firms-xiaomi-vivo-puts-lawyers-in-crosshairs%5C%22%3Eaccusing%3C%2Fa%3E%20them%20of%20using%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20amount%E2%80%9D%20of%20Chinese%20funding%20to%20publish%20%E2%80%9Cpaid%20news%E2%80%9D%20which%20criticised%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20promote%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20Chinese.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPfetcher%20said%20that%20all%20of%20the%20funds%20of%20WMH%2C%20which%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20People%E2%80%99s%20Support%20Foundation%2C%20came%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20US%20businessman%20Neville%20Singham%20Roy%E2%80%99s%20company%20ThoughtWorks%20and%20it%20%E2%80%9Chas%20never%20received%20funds%20from%20a%20foreign%20government%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWMH%E2%80%99s%20investment%20in%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20finalised%20in%20March%202018%2C%20Pfetcher%20said.%20Reputable%20lawyers%20and%20law%20firms%20were%20consulted%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20investment%20%E2%80%9Cstrictly%20followed%20all%20aspects%20of%20Indian%20law%2C%20specifically%20including%20those%20limiting%20foreign%20ownership%20in%20media%20companies%E2%80%9D.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20has%20attended%20various%20shareholder%20meetings%20on%20behalf%20of%20WMH%20but%20nobody%20linked%20to%20the%20for-profit%20company%20has%20%E2%80%9Cever%20influenced%2C%20guided%2C%20or%20directed%20the%20journalistic%20work%E2%80%9D%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFalse%20allegations%20about%20the%20provenance%20of%20the%20funds%20invested%20in%20Newsclick%20continue%20to%20circulate%2C%20despite%20all%20the%20facts%20WMH%20has%20given%20the%20Indian%20authorities.%20These%20dire%20circumstances%20compel%20me%20to%20set%20the%20record%20straight%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20that%20was%20published%20in%20August%2C%20accusing%20Roy%20Singham%20of%20spreading%20Chinese%20propaganda%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20Delhi%20police%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20said%20that%20before%20the%20article%20was%20published%2C%20he%20issued%20a%20statement%20which%20said%20the%20company%20%E2%80%9Chas%20never%20received%20any%20funding%2C%20nor%20taken%20direction%20from%20any%20foreign%20individual%2C%20organization%2C%20political%20party%2C%20or%20government%20(or%20from%20any%20of%20their%20members%20or%20representatives)%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20the%20newspaper%20%E2%80%9Cfailed%20to%20include%E2%80%9D%20and%20instead%20left%20readers%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20source%20of%20Roy%20Singham%E2%80%99s%20funding%20%E2%80%9Cmight%20have%20come%20from%20China%2C%20rather%20than%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20ThoughtWorks%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTheir%20salacious%20headlines%20and%20misleading%20%E2%80%98reporting%E2%80%99%20have%20now%20directly%20contributed%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20innocent%20journalists%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pfetcher%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20repression%20that%20is%20now%20taking%20place%2C%20it%20begs%20the%20question%20as%20to%20whether%20India%20is%20a%20safe%20place%20for%20foreign%20investors%20who%20carefully%20follow%20Indian%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20name%20is%20Jason%20Pfetcher.%20I%20am%20a%20lawyer%20based%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20set%20the%20record%20straight%20regarding%20Worldwide%20Media%20Holdings%20LLC%20(%E2%80%9CWMH%E2%80%9D)%20and%20an%20investment%20made%20by%20WMH%20to%20PPK%20Newsclick%20Studio%20Private%20Limited%20(%E2%80%9CNewsclick%E2%80%9D)%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20an%20attorney%20in%20the%20United%20States%20for%20over%2025%20years.%20For%20many%20years%2C%20I%20worked%20at%20ThoughWorks%2C%20Inc.%2C%20an%20IT%20consultancy%20that%20has%20a%20worldwide%20footprint.%20I%20left%20ThoughtWorks%20in%202017%20when%20the%20company%20was%20sold%20to%20a%20British%20private%20equity%20fund%2C%20Apax%20Partners%20(founded%20in%201969).%20I%20joined%20ThoughtWorks%E2%80%99%20founder%2C%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%20(%E2%80%9CRoy%E2%80%9D)%2C%20to%20assist%20him%20in%20his%20efforts%20to%20give%20away%20most%20of%20the%20proceeds%20he%20received%20from%20the%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20created%20a%20private%20foundation%20in%20the%20United%20States%20called%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Support%20Foundation%2C%20Limited%20(%E2%80%9CPSF%E2%80%9D)%2C%20and%20I%20have%20been%20a%20board%20member%20since%20its%20inception.%20All%20funds%20donated%20to%20PSF%20came%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20ThoughtWorks.%20PSF%20has%20never%20received%20funds%20from%20a%20foreign%20government.%20PSF%20wholly%20owns%20and%20operates%20WMH%2C%20of%20which%20I%20am%20the%20manager.%20WMH%20is%20a%20for-profit%20investment%20vehicle%20which%20has%20made%20various%20investments%20in%20progressive%20media%20projects%20around%20the%20world%20that%20provide%20people-centered%20news%20coverage.%20While%20these%20entities%20are%20consistent%20with%20PSF%E2%80%99s%20mission%2C%20PSF%20seeks%20a%20return%20on%20the%20investments%20we%20make%20in%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToward%20the%20end%20of%202017%2C%20WMH%20identified%20Newsclick%20as%20an%20organization%20that%20was%20consistent%20with%20WMH%E2%80%99s%20purposes%20and%20commenced%20due%20diligence%20on%20a%20potential%20investment%20in%20Newsclick.%20As%20part%20of%20this%20process%2C%20I%20visited%20Delhi%20and%20hired%20local%20counsel%2C%20met%20with%20Newsclick%E2%80%99s%20editor%20and%20other%20Newsclick%20staff%2C%20toured%20its%20facilities%2C%20and%20negotiated%20with%20Newsclick%E2%80%99s%20legal%20counsel.%20Following%20the%20completion%20of%20due%20diligence%2C%20the%20PSF%20board%20determined%20that%20it%20was%20advisable%20that%20WMH%20invest%20in%20Newsclick.%20That%20investment%20was%20finalized%20in%20March%202018.%20While%20I%20have%20attended%20various%20shareholder%20meetings%20of%20Newsclick%20on%20behalf%20of%20WMH%2C%20none%20of%20the%20principals%20of%20PSF%20or%20WMH%2C%20including%20myself%2C%20have%20ever%20influenced%2C%20guided%2C%20or%20directed%20the%20journalistic%20work%20of%20Newsclick.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Newsclick%20investment%20opportunity%20came%20to%20WMH%2C%20in%20part%2C%20from%20our%20relationship%20with%20Prabir%20Purkayastha.%20I%20met%20Prabir%20while%20working%20at%20ThoughtWorks%3B%20we%20were%20fellow%20employees%20there%20for%20many%20years.%20Prabir%20was%2C%20and%20remains%2C%20highly%20regarded%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20technologist%2C%20scientist%2C%20researcher%2C%20and%20business%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Newsclick%E2%80%99s%20offices%20were%20raided%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20which%20accused%20the%20organization%20of%20money%20laundering.%20The%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20subsequently%20initiated%20its%20own%20investigation%2C%20as%20did%20the%20Revenue%20Service%20of%20India.%20Over%20many%20months%2C%20dozens%20of%20Newsclick%E2%80%99s%20journalists%2C%20staff%2C%20and%20other%20associates%2C%20including%20Prabir%20and%20Amit%20Chakraborty%2C%20were%20interrogated%20at%20length%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%2C%20WMH%20has%20provided%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20confirmation%20regarding%20the%20provenance%20of%20the%20funds%20invested%20in%20Newsclick%20by%20WMH.%20WMH%20has%20also%20provided%20ample%20evidence%20that%20it%20is%20and%20has%20always%20been%20in%20good%20standing%20with%20the%20state%20of%20Delaware%20where%20it%20is%20incorporated%2C%20despite%20false%20information%20being%20circulated%20that%20WMH%20was%20a%20defunct%20entity%20when%20it%20invested%20in%20Newsclick.%20Prabir%2C%20along%20with%20Amit%2C%20have%20now%20been%20arrested%20and%20jailed%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20and%20Newsclick%E2%80%99s%20offices%20have%20been%20sealed.%20False%20allegations%20about%20the%20provenance%20of%20the%20funds%20invested%20in%20Newsclick%20continue%20to%20circulate%2C%20despite%20all%20the%20facts%20WMH%20has%20given%20the%20Indian%20authorities.%20These%20dire%20circumstances%20compel%20me%20to%20set%20the%20record%20straight.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20appears%20that%20much%20of%20the%20basis%20for%20this%20action%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20stems%20from%20a%20slanderous%20article%20that%20was%20published%20by%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20on%20August%205%2C%202023.%20Before%20that%20article%20was%20published%2C%20I%20responded%20to%20the%20reporters%E2%80%99%20questions%20on%20behalf%20of%20PSF%20as%20follows%3A%20%E2%80%9CPSF%20has%20never%20received%20any%20funding%2C%20nor%20taken%20direction%20from%20any%20foreign%20individual%2C%20organization%2C%20political%20party%2C%20or%20government%20(or%20from%20any%20of%20their%20members%20or%20representatives).%E2%80%9D%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20failed%20to%20include%20PSF%E2%80%99s%20categorical%20denial%20of%20foreign%20funding%2C%20and%20instead%20left%20readers%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20source%20of%20PSF%E2%80%99s%20funding%20(or%20Roy%E2%80%99s%20for%20that%20matter)%20might%20have%20come%20from%20China%2C%20rather%20than%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20ThoughtWorks.%20Their%20salacious%20headlines%20and%20misleading%20%E2%80%98reporting%E2%80%99%20have%20now%20directly%20contributed%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20innocent%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20traveling%20to%20India%20and%20doing%20business%20there%20for%20nearly%2020%20years.%20I%20recommended%20this%20particular%20investment%20without%20hesitation%2C%20eager%20to%20see%20India%E2%80%99s%20already%20vibrant%20media%20landscape%20be%20made%20even%20more%20so%20by%20the%20growth%20of%20a%20media%20project%20eager%20to%20give%20voice%20to%20the%20voiceless.%20I%20have%20always%20been%20highly%20conscientious%20about%20respecting%20local%20laws.%20Therefore%2C%20reputable%20lawyers%20and%20law%20firms%20were%20consulted%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20investment%20strictly%20followed%20all%20aspects%20of%20Indian%20law%2C%20specifically%20including%20those%20limiting%20foreign%20ownership%20in%20media%20companies.%20Given%20the%20repression%20that%20is%20now%20taking%20place%2C%20it%20begs%20the%20question%20as%20to%20whether%20India%20is%20a%20safe%20place%20for%20foreign%20investors%20who%20carefully%20follow%20Indian%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696656520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F07105239%2F5mtb93eo_neville-roy-singham-1200_625x300_07_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclick-case-no-foreign-funding-neville-roy-singham-company-statement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Worldwide%20Media%20Holdings%20said%20that%20reputable%20lawyers%20and%20law%20firms%20were%20consulted%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20investment%20%26quot%3Bstrictly%20followed%20all%2