%20than%20usual.%20With%20the%20groundwater%20level%20dropping%2C%20the%20tube%20wells%20in%20the%20area%20have%20now%20run%20dry%2C%20forcing%20villages%20to%20rely%20on%20traditional%20wells%20for%20water.%20Access%20to%20treated%20piped%20water%20supply%20remains%20a%20distant%20dream.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDurga%20Puja%2C%20the%20largest%20festival%20in%20the%20state%2C%20is%20less%20than%20a%20month%20away.%20While%20the%20number%20of%20Durga%20Puja%20celebrations%20and%20the%20grandeur%20associated%20with%20them%20have%20been%20steadily%20increasing%20across%20the%20state%20due%20to%20active%20government%20promotion%2C%20the%20festivities%20here%20remain%20subdued.%20Despite%20the%20government%20providing%20Rs%2070%2C000%20to%20Puja%20committees%20and%20subsidised%20electricity%2C%20celebrations%20in%20Saltora%20are%20limited%20to%20just%20three.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20money%2C%20even%20religion%20or%20festivals%20lose%20their%20splendour.%20Saltora%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jiban%20Mondal%2C%20a%20local%20and%20unemployed%20youth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESaltora%20knows%20poverty.%20There%20is%20not%20a%20single%20large%20departmental%20store.%20The%20nearest%20cinema%20hall%20is%2020%20kilometres%20away.%20The%20roads%20are%20worn%20out.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20seems%20like%20hunger%20is%20making%20a%20comeback%20in%20Saltora%20from%20all%20directions.%20This%20is%20Puja%20time%2C%20but%20the%20market%20is%20quiet.%20People%20are%20short%20of%20money%2C%20and%20even%20agriculture%20is%20facing%20difficulties%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Manoj%20Mondal.%20Manoj%20had%20been%20working%20at%20one%20of%20the%20several%20unauthorised%20stone%20quarries%20that%20have%20sprung%20up%20in%20and%20around%20Saltora%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20While%20the%20work%20is%20hazardous%2C%20it%20pays%20well.%20However%2C%20allegations%20of%20illegal%20mining%20often%20leads%20to%20the%20closure%20of%20these%20quarries%2C%20worsening%20the%20locals%E2%80%99%20hardship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESreedhar%20Barui%2C%20a%20community%20elder%2C%20remembers%20the%20hardships%20of%201974.%20%E2%80%9CNeither%20the%20Left%20nor%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government%20managed%20to%20resolve%20our%20water%20scarcity%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06181222%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-20-at-10.52.53-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221038%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06181222%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-20-at-10.52.53-AM.jpeg%201038w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06181222%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-20-at-10.52.53-AM-300x223.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06181222%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-20-at-10.52.53-AM-1024x762.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678700%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22772%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20report%20on%20the%20Anandabazar%20Patrika%2C%20noting%20the%20situation%20of%20hunger%20in%20Bengal%20of%20the%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EFilmmaker%20Ghosh%2C%20too%2C%20remembers%20it%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20time%20of%20despair.%20People%20were%20moving%20in%20large%20numbers%20from%20villages%20to%20cities%2C%20their%20pleas%20for%20sustenance%20rang%20in%20the%20air.%20In%20the%20villages%2C%20community%20kitchens%20were%20a%20lifeline.%20They%20coexisted%20with%20the%20sombre%20sight%20of%20lifeless%20bodies.%20Yet%2C%20in%20the%20cities%2C%20the%20markets%20were%20brimming%20with%20fish%20and%20vegetables.%20We%20tried%20to%20uncover%20the%20reason%20behind%20this%20stark%20contrast%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESaltora%20is%20rich%20in%20mineral%20resources%2C%20including%20coal%2C%20copper%2C%20gas%2C%20quartzite%2C%20and%20granite%2C%20yet%20no%20substantial%20efforts%20have%20been%20made%20to%20tap%20into%20these%20abundant%20resources.%20The%20local%20Panchayat%20office%20is%20the%20busiest%20place%20in%20the%20area%2C%20where%20people%20often%20troop%20to%2C%20to%20access%20various%20government%20incentive%20schemes.%20Behind%20the%20office%20stands%20Biharinath%20Hill%2C%20named%20after%20the%20local%20deity%20associated%20with%20nature%20and%20hills%2C%20seemingly%20bearing%20witness%20to%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20years%20between%201967%20and%201974%20were%20cruel%20for%20Saltora%20and%20are%20part%20of%20public%20memory.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENazibur%20Rahman%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20the%20area%2C%20recounted%20something%20similar%20to%20what%20Ghosh%20remembered%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20villagers%20were%20trapped%20between%20oppressive%20landlords%20and%20exploitative%20moneylenders.%20We%20had%20to%20mortgage%20valuable%20possessions%2C%20from%20utensils%20to%20land%2C%20just%20to%20survive.%20By%201972%2C%20most%20common%20people%20were%20left%20with%20nothing.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20rainfall%20meant%20there%20was%20no%20way%20to%20make%20a%20living%20through%20agriculture.%20Starvation%20became%20a%20grim%20reality.%20Many%20people%20succumbed%20to%20hunger.%20Langar%20kitchens%20were%20set%20up%2C%20and%20we%20all%20used%20to%20stand%20in%20line%20to%20receive%20our%20portion%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekhichuri%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20these%20communal%20kitchens.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuralidhar%20Pramanik%2C%20a%20volunteer%20at%20one%20of%20these%20communal%20kitchens%2C%20recalled%2C%20%E2%80%9CMissionaries%20ran%20those%20kitchens%2C%20and%20we%2C%20the%20young%20men%20from%20the%20village%2C%20worked%20there%20to%20prepare%20khichdi.%20It%20was%20a%20tough%20time.%20Government-run%20community%20kitchens%20were%20a%20bit%20far%2C%20and%20they%20were%20often%20overcrowded.%20Desperate%2C%20people%20travelled%20from%20one%20village%20to%20another%20just%20to%20get%20food.%20Many%20months%20passed%20with%20people%20eating%20%3Cem%3Ekhichuri%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20their%20only%20meal.%20I%20witnessed%20people%20lying%20dead%20on%20the%20streets.%20It%E2%80%99s%20been%20almost%2050%20years%2C%20but%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20forget%20those%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGhosh%20notes%20that%20this%20picture%20is%20not%20as%20far%20back%20in%20the%20past%20as%20the%20village%20would%20have%20liked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20now%2C%20after%20fifty%20years%2C%20the%20memories%20of%20the%20film%20from%20the%20past%20resonate.%20Part%20of%20the%20village%20has%20gained%20economic%20prosperity%2C%20but%20the%20backward%20classes%20still%20struggle%20in%20the%20darkness.%20Their%20condition%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20to%20the%20news%20unless%20some%20disaster%20or%20tragedy%20strikes%2C%20or%20if%20they%20turn%20to%20extremism%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ghosh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06181306%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-20-at-10.52.23-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22973%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06181306%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-20-at-10.52.23-AM.jpeg%20973w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06181306%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-20-at-10.52.23-AM-300x185.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678703%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGautam%20Ghosh.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%201970s%2C%20Ghosh%20had%20spent%20his%20savings%20to%20buy%20a%20hand-held%20Pillard%20camera%20for%20Rs%202%2C500%20and%20taken%20off%20for%20Bankura%20district.%20He%20saw%20and%20showed%20the%20struggles%20of%20individuals%20teetering%20on%20the%20fringes%20of%20society%2C%20a%20topic%20he%20would%20dwell%20on%20further%20in%20his%20feature%20films.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20film%20was%20produced%20by%20the%20Joris%20Ivens%20Collective%2C%20a%20group%20named%20after%20the%20legendary%20Dutch%20documentary%20filmmaker.%20With%20narration%20by%20actors%20Aparna%20Sen%20and%20Jagannath%20Guha%20and%20made%20on%20a%20tight%20budget%2C%20the%20film%20faced%20challenges%20and%20had%20to%20be%20halted%20until%20another%20legendary%20filmmaker%2C%20Mrinal%20Sen%2C%20stepped%20in.%20Sen%20arranged%20for%20a%20bank%20loan%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20and%20stood%20as%20guarantor.%20The%20film%20went%20on%20to%20win%20an%20award%20at%20the%20Oberhausen%20Film%20Festival.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20the%20film%20remains%20relevant%20today%20because%20cinema%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20memories%20of%20time.%20It%20vividly%20portrayed%20life%20in%20Saltora%20and%20Kalagachhia%20half%20a%20century%20ago%2C%20seamlessly%20blending%20reporting%20and%20in-depth%20analysis%20of%20its%20underlying%20causes.%20While%20it%20garnered%20numerous%20awards%20at%20international%20film%20festivals%2C%20here%20in%20our%20country%2C%20we%20had%20to%20resort%20to%20using%20projectors%20to%20showcase%20it%20in%20various%20universities%20after%20the%20Emergency.%20The%20creation%20of%20this%20documentary%20itself%20is%20a%20compelling%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ghosh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696649543000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06181254%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-20-at-10.51.08-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhungry-autumn-bengal-village-gautam-ghosh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Filmmaker%20Gautam%20Ghosh's%20first%20film%20had%20given%20unparalleled%20visibility%20to%20the%20forgotten%201974%20famine%20in%20the%20state%20and%20questioned%20the%20success%20of%20modern%20agriculture%20and%20industry.%20How%20is%20the%20village%20in%20which%20it%20is%20set%20doing%20today%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhungry-autumn-bengal-village-gautam-ghosh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20tribute%20to%20M%20S%20Swaminathan%3A%20A%20true%20'farmers'%20scientist'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696646152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-09%2F28%2Ffull%2F1695885132-4221.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fa-tribute-to-m-s-swaminathan-a-true-farmers-scientist-123100601492_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Swaminathan%20has%20nurtured%20countless%20minds%2C%20instilling%20in%20them%20a%20passion%20for%20learning%20and%20innovation%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fa-tribute-to-m-s-swaminathan-a-true-farmers-scientist-123100601492_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fa-tribute-to-m-s-swaminathan-a-tru