0single%20mother%2C%20I%20want%20my%20daughter%20to%20be%20able%20to%20differentiate%20between%20right%20and%20wrong.%20We%20also%20have%20programmes%20for%20parents%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEITA%2C%20she%20says%2C%20is%20a%20holistic%20solution%20for%20children.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20us%20are%20today%20working%20in%20fields%20which%20are%20miles%20away%20from%20what%20we%20studied.%20We%20want%20this%20to%20be%20an%20early%20intervention%20for%20kids%20to%20bridge%20all%20the%20gaps%20in%20the%20education%20system.%20Learning%20to%20express%20yourself%20is%20a%20very%20important%20skill%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20profession%20you%20choose%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%20June%202023%2C%20the%20centre%20has%20had%20a%20phenomenal%20response%20so%20far%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founder.%20Their%20group%20sessions%20are%20a%20great%20hit.%20They%20have%20conducted%20sessions%20like%20%E2%80%98Her%20Canvas%3A%20Art%20Journaling%20for%20Women%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Our%20Game%20of%20Hope%E2%80%99%20(interactive%20games%20for%20adults).%20They%20are%20planning%20to%20launch%20online%20support%20groups%20on%2010%20October%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPooja%20wants%20The%20Love%20Hope%20Company%20to%20become%20the%20go-to%20mental%20health%20space%20throughout%20the%20country%2C%20both%20offline%20and%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1696427515.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Comfortable%20spaces%20for%20therapy%20at%20The%20Love%20Hope%20Company.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1696427515.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1696427515-300x157.jp