o%20Club%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F77487%2Fbengaluru-startup-eco-friendly-wedding-cards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBengaluru-based%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20created%20a%20circular%20economy%20by%20lending%20baby-use%20products%20on%20a%20subscription%20basis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20memories%20while%20being%20sustainable%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%20January%202022%2C%20and%20currently%20operable%20only%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20company%20has%20received%20an%20overwhelming%20response%20from%20parents%20dealing%20with%20similar%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPruthvi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20have%20worked%20in%20the%20marketing%20industry%20for%20some%20time%2C%20I%20had%20always%20been%20interested%20in%20becoming%20an%20entrepreneur.%20Gro%20Club%20is%20a%20passion%20project%20as%20it%20marries%20both%20sustainability%20and%20entrepreneurship.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20idea%20of%20Gro%20Club%20brewed%2C%20Pruthvi%20turned%20towards%20his%20friends%20Hrishikesh%20H%20S%2C%20Roopesh%20Shah%20and%20Sapna%20M%20S%20for%20support.%20%E2%80%9CHrishikesh%20and%20I%20worked%20together%20on%20my%20previous%20venture%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20is%20his%20dream%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFour%20of%20us%20are%20parents%20of%20kids%20between%205%20and%2014%20years%20of%20age.%20They%20could%20relate%20to%20the%20problem%20of%20them%20outgrowing%20things%20too.%20Apart%20from%20that%2C%20all%20of%20us%20believed%20that%20with%20our%20startup%2C%20we%20could%20pitch-in%20and%20reduce%20the%20mounting%20trash%20in%20the%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETerming%20products%20such%20as%20bicycles%2C%20cribs%2C%20bunk%20beds%20and%20strollers%20as%20single-use%20products%2C%20Pruthvi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9C