%3EAfter%20returning%20from%20Israel%2C%20he%20established%20a%20dairy%20farm%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327249%2Fkota-engineer-runs-sustainable-dairy-farm-saves-on-electricy-bills-gau-organics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGau%20Organics%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20hometown%20with%20his%20brothers%2C%20Uttam%20Jyot%20and%20Gagandeep.%20Through%20this%20business%2C%20he%20sells%20milk%20and%20other%20dairy%20products%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20butter%2C%20organic%20jaggery%2C%20honey%2C%20cow%20dung%20cakes%2C%20manures%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20what%E2%80%99s%20unique%20about%20this%20dairy%20farm%20is%20its%20sustainability%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20farm%20produces%2070%20percent%20of%20its%20own%20electricity%20using%20waste.%20When%20Singh%20realised%20that%20the%20electricity%20cost%20on%20the%20farm%20was%20way%20too%20high%2C%20he%20came%20up%20with%20a%20sustainable%20alternative%20to%20have%20a%20self-sustained%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20he%20installed%20two%20biogas%20plants%20of%2040%20KW%20in%20his%2050-acre%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321571%2Famith-kishan-quits-job-to-start-hebbuvu-organic-and-natural-farming-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edairy%20farm%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20this%2C%20he%20generates%20Rs%201.5%E2%80%931.8%20lakh-worth%20electricity%20every%20month.%20%E2%80%9CRight%20now%2C%20we%20are%20producing%2080%20KW%20of%20power%20uninterrupted%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20they%20collect%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine%20and%20send%20it%20to%20the%20digester%20of%20these%20biogas%20plants.%20It%20is%20then%20converted%20into%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20way%20Gau%20Organics%20is%20thinking%20of%20a%20sustainable%2